          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-876 test: several improvement to ost-pool.sh",
        "message": "LU-876 test: several improvement to ost-pool.sh\n\nFix a bug in the output parsing of createmany in test 18 causing\ncrazy results like this:\nAvg time taken for 30000 creates without pool: 1322089193.67\nAvg time taken for 30000 creates with pool: 1322089359.43\nAvg time taken for 30000 creates with missing pool: 1322089580.10\n\ncreatemany actually prints several lines when creating more than 10k\nfiles, causing this bug.\nTest 18 has also been changed to create a less files when SLOW=no\nsince this test currently take ~30min to complete with the default\nparameters.\nTest 14 is another one taking a lot of time and it is because it\nfills up OST0 with dd, so the usual size check to skip this test has\nbeen added.\n\nSigned-off-by: Johann Lombardi <johann@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I887c3eb86b2e6103aef62f4d059c6fe3d355e719\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
